data.description: Excited to present a great  corner lot home in a convenient location of Apopka, FL. The home built in 2014 by the current home owners has a great open floor plan living area with the kitchen looking out to the 26x10 family room, dining room and a breakfast area. The kitchen is upgraded with granite counter tops, tons of wood cabinetry and newer slate appliances. The living room has built in surround speakers enhancing your television viewing experience. The large master bedroom has a walk-in closet, dual sinks, a large garden tub and a separate stall shower.  THE ROOF HAS SOLAR PANELS LOWERING ELECTRIC BILLS. Enjoy Florida living in your covered and screened back porch. Also included a Huge 2-car garage, upgraded landscaping with lighting, rain gutters and indoor laundry room. Very Low HOA.The home is located conveniently near the 429, Maitland exchange and 436/441.  Stop and schedule your appointment today.
